    // About
    section#about
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2.section-heading.text-uppercase About
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted Simply the best in teaching languages.  Our school is on the top in the rankings of language schools in Krak√≥w.
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            ul.timeline
              li
                .timeline-image
                  img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='images/about/1.jpg', alt='')
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 December 2013
                    h4.subheading Our journey began! 
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | We established our school in old tenement house in the city center. It consists of small reception and literally one classroom.
              li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                  img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='images/about/2.jpg', alt='')
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 March 2014
                    h4.subheading First semester in MultiLingua School started.
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | In the begining 10 students started to learnd english at 3 different lveles B1, B2 and C1. At the time we had just 3 employees.
              li
                .timeline-image
                  img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='images/about/3.jpg', alt='')
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 August 2016
                    h4.subheading New languages in our courses.
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | Due to high demand we decided to add to our offer German and Spanis languages.  We hired new teachers. At that time from our School graduated 600 students.
              li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                  img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='images/about/4.jpg', alt='')
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 March 2017
                    h4.subheading New classrooms and fast growth.
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | We rented out 2 more rooms in the same location. At that time our school had 6 employees. Winter semester 2016/2017 started 240 new students!
              li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                  h4
                    | Be Part
                    br
                    | Of Our
                    br
                    | Story!
